news.title: Telangana government's revenue from property registrations rises 3% in November 2024
news.para: According to the chief minister's office, while the revenue through property registrations was 1,127 crore from 1.05 lakh documents in Nov last, the registration department received 1,160 crore from 1.19 lakh documents this Nov.

news.title: Amazon India acquires Lodha’s 38-acre land parcel for 450 crore in Palava
news.para: As part of the deal, Amazon’s India subsidiary Amazon Data Services India will also get access to the already sanctioned floor space index—permissible development potential—of around 4.16 million sq ft.

news.title: Gurugram's air quality worsens as construction continues despite GRAP restrictions
news.para: The air quality index (AQI) was recorded at 226 (poor) on Tuesday. At a reading of 267, Teri Gram was the worst hit, followed by Sector 51 (254), and Gwalpahari (247) -- all in the ‘poor' category.

news.title: Yeida hi-tech township near Jewar airport sees over 34,000 registrations
news.para: The township, which promises state-of-the-art amenities and enhanced living standards for residents in the region, will offer 451 residential plots in various sizes.

news.title: Karnataka HC orders razing of 15-floor building in Bengaluru
news.para: The high court recently directed the Bangalore Development Authority (BDA) commissioner to prepare a plan for evacuation and demolition of the 15-floor ‘A' Wing/Block of Platinum City in Peenya to ensure that the development is in compliance with applicable laws.

news.title: Uttar Pradesh government revises norms for commercial land allotment
news.para: The new guidelines are expected to enhance transparency in the commercial land allocation process,

news.title: Jaiprakash Associates makes Rs 16,000 crore settlement offer to avoid bankruptcy
news.para: JAL said an initial upfront payment - of about ₹4,000 crore - will not be made immediately, but only after nine months from the date lenders agree to the settlement, people aware of the details said.

news.title: SC summons Nagpur collector, tehsildar in Nirmal Nagari's MahaRERA registration case
news.para: The apex court has summoned Nagpur collector and tehsildar to appear before it on December 19, demanding a status update on actions following a warrant issued by MahaRera.

news.title: DLF appoints Badal Bagri as CFO
news.para: Badal Bagri's appointment as CFO is effective December 6, DLF said in a stock exchange filing.

news.title: ED seizes luxury cars, bank deposits in raids against Orris Infrastructure & Three C Shelters
news.para: The FDs and BGs, totalling Rs 31.22 crore, held in the name of the Orris group of companies, have been frozen and seized.

news.title: Noida authority flags illegal constructions along Yamuna floodplains
news.para: In addition, the authority has turned its attention to Kondli village, where the construction of several buildings has been noted. To determine further action, the authority sought a detailed report on these structures.

news.title: SC refuses to relax GRAP stage IV curbs until AQI shows improvement in Delhi
news.para: Observing the Delhi-NCR faced a similar situation every year between October and December, the bench proposed to go into all aspects that cause air pollution and find a permanent solution.

news.title: Cochin development body delays repairs for Mundamveli apartments
news.para: Residents launched protests against GCDA after leakages were reported in the building months ago, but the authority is unable to carry out major repair works as the technical committee of state govt is yet to approve the repair works.

news.title: Dharavi redevelopment project to use drones and LiDAR technology for digital survey
news.para: Drones and remote sensing technology Light Detection and Ranging (LiDAR) are being used to map the 620 acres densely populated Dharavi slums. This is to ensure accuracy, transparency, and efficiency in a redevelopment project of this scale and complexity.

news.title: Andhra Pradesh government approves Visakhapatnam metro rail project phase I
news.para: ​​The first phase will consist of three corridors: Steel Plant Junction to Kommadi (34.40 km), Gurudwara to Old Post Office Junction (5.08 km), and Thatichetlapalem to Chinna Waltair (6.75 km).

news.title: House prices in UK rise 3.7% in November 2024: Nationwide
news.para: Prices rose by 3.7% in November compared with the same month last year, Nationwide said, significantly faster than October's 2.4% increase and the biggest jump since November 2022.

news.title: Vietnam court upholds death sentence for property tycoon in $27 billion fraud case
news.para: Property developer Truong My Lan, 68, was convicted this year of swindling money from Saigon Commercial Bank (SCB) -- which prosecutors said she controlled -- and sentenced to death for fraud totalling $27 billion.

news.title: CRDA clears sanction of funds for construction of major buildings in Amaravati
news.para: CRDA on Monday decided to call for tenders for various works worth Rs 11,467 crore including the construction of major buildings, in the capital region of Amaravati.

news.title: Uttar Pradesh: 76 lifts registered under new lift act
news.para: ​​ Out of these, 14 lifts were registered in GB Nagar and 7 were registered in Ghaziabad - these include 1 residential, 5 commercial and 1 industrial lift.

news.title: Kerala HC directs state government to examine violations of registry and patta conditions
news.para: The bench of Justices A K Jayasankaran Nambiar and K V Jayakumar issued the directive in response to a petition filed by P B Satheesh, director of Nerkazhcha, a Thrissur-based association.
